<exploration xml:id="warm-cuantosVes-muchasManerasMostrar" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Cuántos ves: Muchas maneras de mostrar 5</title>

<statement>
  <p>
    <line>¿Cuántos ves?</line>
    <line>¿Cómo lo sabes?, ¿qué ves?</line>
  </p>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-141788">
    <shortdescription>un punto</shortdescription>
  </image>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-141789">
    <shortdescription>un punto</shortdescription>
  </image>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-141790">
    <shortdescription>un punto</shortdescription>
  </image>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses:</p>
<ul>
      <li>5: There are 3 black dots and 2 white dots.</li>
      <li>5: There are 4 dots on top and 1 on the bottom.</li>
      <li>5: The 5-frame is full. There are 4 black dots and 1 white dot, just like the last picture.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


